Before we can patch and compile glibc you will first have to download and install Stuart WinterÂ´s slackkit-*-arm-1.txz.
From here: https://slackware.uk/slackwarearm/slackwarearm-devtools/slackkit/pkgs/

And we also have to download slackware64-15.0/source/l/glibc with rsync

As root
   # cd /usr/src
   # wget https://slackware.uk/slackwarearm/slackwarearm-devtools/slackkit/pkgs/slackkit-1.40-arm-1.txz
   # installpkg slackkit-1.40-arm-1.txz

   # cd /root
   # mkdir -p slackware64-current/source/l/glibc/
   # cd slackware64-current/source/l/glibc/

As we only need and want glibc directory
Sync the Slackware/x86_64 tree for glibc:
   # rsync -Pavv ftp.slackware.org.uk::slackware/slackware64-15.0/patches/source/glibc/ .
   
This is the old way, Please read the New Way below as Stuart was kind to edit this to the origenal script.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Now go to the directory where you have your downloaded my glibc slackbuild with the patches.
In this example i have the glibc directory under /usr/src
   # cd /usr/src/glibc/
   
Copy the patches to "/root/slackware64-current/source/l/glibc/" directory
   # cp patches/* /root/slackware64-current/source/l/glibc/

And now we can compile glibc
   # ./arm/build
 
Packages will be stored under "/root/tgzstash"
   # cd /root/tgzstash
   # upgradepkg a/aaa_glibc-solibs-2.33-arm-8p1_slack15.0.txz l/glibc-2.33-arm-8p1_slack15.0.txz

New Way
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In this example i have the glibc directory under /root
   # cd /root
   # mkdir -p slackwarearm-15.0/patches/source/glibc/
   # cd slackwarearm-15.0/patches/source/glibc/

As we only need and want glibc directory
Sync the Slackware arm tree for glibc:
   # rsync -Pavv ftp.slackware.org.uk::slackwarearm/slackwarearm-15.0/patches/source/glibc/ .

And now we can compile glibc
   # BUILD_PLUGINS=Widevine ./arm/build

Packages will be stored under "/root/tgzstash"
   # cd /root/tgzstash
   # upgradepkg a/aaa_glibc-solibs-2.33-arm-8p1_slack15.0.txz l/glibc-2.33-arm-8p1_slack15.0.txz

And you are all done.
